## Feature 1: Intelligent OCR Capture (Single & Bulk Processing)
This is the core feature of the platform. It handles image intake, API payload structuring, and contact json normalization.

### 1.1 Use Case Diagram (Capture Module)
```mermaid
usecaseDiagram
    actor PersonalUser as Personal User
    actor EnterpriseUser as Enterprise User
    
    usecase "Upload Image(s)" as UC1
    usecase "Validate File Size" as UC2
    usecase "Extract Contact Data" as UC3
    usecase "Normalize Schema" as UC4
    usecase "Store to SQLite" as UC5
    usecase "Deduct Quota" as UC6
    
    PersonalUser --> UC1
    EnterpriseUser --> UC1
    
    UC1 ..> UC2 : <<include>>
    UC1 ..> UC3 : <<include>>
    UC3 ..> UC4 : <<include>>
    UC4 ..> UC5 : <<include>>
    EnterpriseUser ..> UC6 : <<extend>>
```

### 1.2 Activity Diagram (Capture Workflow)
```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> ImageReceived
    ImageReceived --> CheckRateLimit
    CheckRateLimit --> EnsureQuota: Valid Token
    EnsureQuota --> FetchEngineStatus: Quota OK
    FetchEngineStatus --> ExtractData
    ExtractData --> NormalizeData: Raw JSON from LLM
    NormalizeData --> CalculateDealScore
    CalculateDealScore --> SaveContact
    SaveContact --> [*]: 200 OK Return
```

### 1.3 Sequence / Interaction Diagram (Multi-Card Parse)
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as /api/scan-multi
    participant DB as SQLite
    participant LLM as AI Wrapper
    
    Client->>API: POST Base64 Group Photo
    API->>DB: Check group_scans_used
    DB-->>API: Quota = 3/9999
    API->>LLM: Pass Image + Bulk Prompt
    LLM-->>API: Returns Array of 5 Contacts
    loop For Each Contact
        API->>API: normalizeCard()
        API->>DB: INSERT INTO contacts
    end
    API-->>Client: Return 5 Contact Profiles
```

