## Feature 3: Smart Calendar & Scheduling Engine
Allows users to instantly schedule follow-ups and invite attendees via automated email triggers.

### 3.1 Class Diagram (Calendar Module)
```mermaid
classDiagram
    class CalendarEvent {
        +int id
        +string title
        +string description
        +datetime start_date
        +datetime end_date
        +createEvent()
        +deleteEvent()
    }
    class EventAttendee {
        +int event_id
        +string email
        +string status
        +sendInvite()
    }
    class NodemailerMailer {
        +string smtp_host
        +string smtp_port
        +dispatch()
    }
    
    CalendarEvent "1" *-- "many" EventAttendee : has
    EventAttendee ..> NodemailerMailer : triggers
```

### 3.2 Activity Diagram (Event Deletion & SMTP Protection)
```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> UserClicksDelete
    UserClicksDelete --> CustomReactModal
    CustomReactModal --> APIRequest: User Confirms
    APIRequest --> DB_Delete_Record
    
    DB_Delete_Record --> TriggerEmailCancellation
    state TriggerEmailCancellation {
        [*] --> SendSMTP
        SendSMTP --> SMTP_Success
        SendSMTP --> SMTP_Crash
        SMTP_Crash --> CatchErrorSilently
    }
    TriggerEmailCancellation --> ReturnSuccessToUI
    ReturnSuccessToUI --> [*]
```

