## Feature 4: Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) & SuperAdmin Control Panel
Distinct capabilities between Freemium users and Enterprise deployment.

### 4.1 Use Case Diagram (Platform Security)
```mermaid
usecaseDiagram
    actor Personal as Personal
    actor Enterprise as Enterprise
    actor SuperAdmin as Platform Admin
    
    usecase "View Personal Contacts" as V1
    usecase "Export to CSV" as V2
    usecase "Deploy/Pause AI Engines" as V3
    usecase "View Global Telemetry" as V4
    
    Personal --> V1
    Enterprise --> V1
    Enterprise --> V2
    
    SuperAdmin --> V3
    SuperAdmin --> V4
```

### 4.2 Sequence Diagram (Admin Deploying Models)
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant SuperAdmin
    participant UI as Management Dashboard
    participant API as /api/admin/models
    participant DB as ai_models Table
    
    SuperAdmin->>UI: Click "Pause" on Gemini Engine
    UI->>API: PUT status = 'paused'
    note over API: Restrict via requireSuperAdmin JWT
    API->>DB: UPDATE ai_models SET status='paused' WHERE id=1
    DB-->>API: Confirmation
    API-->>UI: 200 Success
    
    note over UI: Later when User Scans...
    API->>DB: Check Status
    DB-->>API: Status = 'paused'
    API-->>User: 503 Models Disabled Alert
```

