## Feature 5: AI Networking Coach & Campaign Autowriter
The intelligent analytical suite that warns users about stale connections and writes automated cold-emails.

### 5.1 Use Case Diagram (Analytics Suite)
```mermaid
usecaseDiagram
    actor User as Any User
    
    usecase "Load Analytics Dashboard" as Load
    usecase "Calculate Stale Connections" as Calc1
    usecase "Determine Missing Context" as Calc2
    usecase "Generate Actionable Insights" as Gen
    usecase "Auto-Write Campaign Draft" as Draft
    
    User --> Load
    Load ..> Calc1 : <<include>>
    Load ..> Calc2 : <<include>>
    Calc1 ..> Gen : Feed to LLM
    Gen ..> Draft : <<extend>> (User clicks CTA)
```

### 5.2 Activity Diagram (Coach Insight Generation)
```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> DashboardMounts
    DashboardMounts --> FetchAllUserContacts
    FetchAllUserContacts --> FilterLogic
    
    state FilterLogic {
        [*] --> CheckDates
        CheckDates --> MarkStale(>14days)
        CheckDates --> CheckFields
        CheckFields --> MarkMissingContext
    }
    
    FilterLogic --> LLMPromptCreation
    LLMPromptCreation --> generateWithFallback
    generateWithFallback --> ReturnJSON
    ReturnJSON --> RenderGamifiedLeaderboard
    RenderGamifiedLeaderboard --> [*]
```
